<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.2">
<l>kavvaivā ḷeyiṟṟu vaṉpēyk katirmulai cuvaitti laṅkai</l>
<l>vavviya viṭumpai tīrak kaṭuṅkaṇai turanta ventai</l>
<l>kovvaivāy makaḷir koṅkaik kuṅkumaṅ kaḻuvip pōnta</l>
<l>teyvanīr kamaḻum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who, having sucked the swollen breast of the powerful, loud demon</l>
<l rend="indent">with sword[-like] teeth,</l>
<l>Sent a swift arrow to end the suffering that had taken hold of Lanka,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr where sacred waters,</l>
<l>Which keep washing the kumkuma from breasts of ladies</l>
<l rend="indent">with kovvai [fruit] lips, scent [the air].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
